import React, { Component } from 'react' import _ from 'lodash' import { Table, Progress } from 'semantic-ui-react' import Pagination from './Pagination' import './index.scss' class TableExamplePagination extends Component { getSerialNo = index => { return (_.get(this.props.data, 'pageNo') - 1) * 10 + index } deleteCampaign = id => { console.log('id of campaign is here', id) } render() { const { data, headers, onPageChange, loading } = this.props if (!data) { return null } const { campaigns } = data return (
{headers && ( {headers.map(header => ( {header.value} ))} )} {campaigns && campaigns.map((part, index) => ( {this.getSerialNo(index + 1)} {_.capitalize(part.name)} {_.capitalize(part.campaignType)} {_.capitalize(part.status)} {_.capitalize(part.deviceType)} Impression : 70% Click : 90% Bounce :10% Browse: 70% this.deleteCampaign(part.campaignId)} /> ))}
) } } export default TableExamplePagination
